==原本的恆星==
在[[密接聯星|密近]][[聯星|雙星]][[雙星系統|系統]]（靠得很近的雙星）中，較輕的恆星會轉移質量至另一顆伴星。（參見[[聯星#質量傳輸和吸積|聯星#質量傳輸和吸積]]/[[X射线脉冲星|X射线脉冲星]]）The shrinking star can then become a planetary-mass object. An example is a Jupiter-mass object orbiting the [[pulsar|pulsar]] PSR J1719-1438.<ref>{{cite journal |arxiv=1108.5201 |bibcode=2011Sci...333.1717B |doi=10.1126/science.1208890 |title=Transformation of a Star into a Planet in a Millisecond Pulsar Binary |year=2011 |last1=Bailes |first1=M. |last2=Bates |first2=S. D. |last3=Bhalerao |first3=V. |last4=Bhat |first4=N. D. R. |last5=Burgay |first5=M. |last6=Burke-Spolaor |first6=S. |last7=d'Amico |first7=N. |last8=Johnston |first8=S. |last9=Keith |first9=M. J. |journal=Science |volume=333 |issue=6050 |pages=1717–20 |pmid=21868629}}</ref>

== 衛星型行星和星盤行星 ==

有些較大型的衛星，例如木星的[[伽利略衛星|伽利略衛星]]或者土星的[[土衛六|土衛六]]，他們的大小接近甚至超越[[水星|水星]]。[[阿兰·斯特恩|阿兰·斯特恩]]認為星體應否被定義成行星只應視乎其物理特性而無關其位置，並提出了'''[[衛星型行星|衛星型行星]]'''這個字來稱呼她們。以這個概念，斯特恩認為[[小行星帶|小行星帶]]和[[凱伯帶|凱伯帶]]的矮行星也應被算作行星。<ref name="satelliteplanet">{{cite web |url=http://news.discovery.com/space/should-large-moons-be-called-satellite-planets.html#post-a-comment |title=Should Large Moons Be Called 'Satellite Planets'? |publisher=News.discovery.com |date=2010-05-14 |accessdate=2011-11-04 |archive-date=2012-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505221146/http://news.discovery.com/space/should-large-moons-be-called-satellite-planets.html#post-a-comment |dead-url=no }}</ref>

